es the inhomogeneous Pr crystal field level splitting so that inter-site\ninteractions become irrelevant for $x=0.97$. The structural complexity for the\nA-site may be reflected in the hysteretic uniform magnetization of B-site\nruthenium in the N\\'{e}el phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2014 17:53:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
